{"tid":2054892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實「罷工罷課公投」係乜嘢嚟？有冇人知？","createTime":"2020-06-07T13:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T04:33:33.000Z","uid":221035,"like":87,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a895ce736ed937bca8a1c3dd56319e4a1176ee","tid":2054892,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事源</span></ins></span></div><br />\n國安法即將殺到，二百萬三罷聯合陣線23個工會於昨日(6/6)聯同中學生罷課平台召開記招，宣佈於14/6發起三罷公投。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pB9H73P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpB9H73P.jpg&h=4fbe41d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公投計劃內容</span></ins></span></div><br />\n公投將於14/6發起，當天會進行兩項公投。<br />\n第一項是罷工公投，投票對象係該23名工會嘅會員，由於對象只為工會會員，因此投票前必先加入公會；第二項是罷課公投，投票對象係全港中學生，會用實體票認證學生身份。時間地點稍後公佈！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJvTu7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJvTu7n.jpg&h=7675f177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公投程序</span>：</ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">若你是打工仔</span><br />\n1. 加入工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/305DVqj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F305DVqj&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=3977186e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/305DVqj</a><br />\n2. 當日參與公投<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">若你是中學生</span><br />\n1. 帶同學生證明<br />\n2. 當日參與公投<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公投通過條件/目標</span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工公投</span><br />\n條件1: <br />\n6萬人參與公投，6成人支持罷工行動。<br />\n條件2: <br />\n各工會自定人數門檻，8成工會達標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">罷課公投</span><br />\n條件1:<br />\n全港10000名中學生參與公投。<br />\n條件2:<br />\n六成人支持罷課行動。<br />\n<br />\n若同時達成2個條件，就會啓動<span style=\"color: red;\">聯合罷工計劃！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yg5HowK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYg5HowK.jpg&h=8fbbcae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聯合三罷計劃：</span></ins><br />\n第一階段：<br />\n- 3日警示式罷工，可以用各方式加入罷工，例如SL....AL....blablabla<br />\n<br />\n第二階段：<br />\n- 真三罷<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>Q&amp;A時間：</ins></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：現時工會人數幾多？6萬人死線係幾時？</span><br />\nA：23個工會會員人數近1萬，要6萬人其實唔係冇機會，大家記唔記得2月初醫護罷工？當時HAEA嘅會員人數兩星期內由1000左右增加到20000人，係HA嘅四份之一員工！死線係公投當日！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：罷工有無保障？</span><br />\nA :  政治罷工法例無保障，所以人數越多保障越大，夠多人佢冇可能炒哂你哋！呢個亦都係點解罷工前要搞公投！工會會提供一切法律/資金支援！btw港共都唔係同你講法律㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：唔夠6萬係咪會提早失敗？公投會唔會犯限聚令？</span><br />\nA :  公投日亦會招收會員，不會宣佈提早失敗。公投除咗表態是否罷工，亦向國際社會表達民意。公投會分流，票站多於一個。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>結語：</ins></span></span></div><br />\n大三罷係反對國安法嘅最後機會，請各位手足團結一次！<br />\n<br />\n知道大家對三罷冇咩信心，但今次同9.2 9.3 11.11 嘅三罷係好大分別！今次三罷係由工會/學生組織發起，並且有公投作為人數保證，效果係前所未有！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有睇新聞都知，政府今日發咗篇聲明，瘋狂狙擊個公投。正所謂敵人反對嘅我哋更加要做，大家快啲spread個公投出去！！"},{"pid":"d29ae7b0f78a865faf97288028f5754075ff8f01","tid":2054892,"uid":223643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"大家快啲了解一下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6172123ccad3e4ee759c0d21d6f4962d6a3131","tid":2054892,"uid":221035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"大家可憐吓我，幫我推下post，出咗幾個都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4339c619dbc69c070dce27c403856141bb461a1","tid":2054892,"uid":47101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d004958b6d03caee07aca86e074b369f05460807","tid":2054892,"uid":260964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1a895ce736ed937bca8a1c3dd56319e4a1176ee","tid":2054892,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事源</span></ins></span></div><br />\n國安法即將殺到，二百萬三罷聯合陣線23個工會於昨日(6/6)聯同中學生罷課平台召開記招，宣佈於14/6發起三罷公投。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pB9H73P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpB9H73P.jpg&h=4fbe41d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公投計劃內容</span></ins></span></div><br />\n公投將於14/6發起，當天會進行兩項公投。<br />\n第一項是罷工公投，投票對象係該23名工會嘅會員，由於對象只為工會會員，因此投票前必先加入公會；第二項是罷課公投，投票對象係全港中學生，會用實體票認證學生身份。時間地點稍後公佈！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJvTu7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJvTu7n.jpg&h=7675f177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公投程序</span>：</ins><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">若你是打工仔</span><br />\n1. 加入工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/305DVqj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F305DVqj&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=3977186e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/305DVqj</a><br />\n2. 當日參與公投<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">若你是中學生</span><br />\n1. 帶同學生證明<br />\n2. 當日參與公投<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;